		<description>&lt;p&gt;Spanish speakers who are using &lt;a href="http://linkedin.com" target="_blank"&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; will be happy to know that this business social network now &lt;a href="http://blog.linkedin.com/blog/2008/07/linkedin-la-r-1.html" target="_blank"&gt;supports two languages: English and Spanish&lt;/a&gt;. You can choose the language from the drop down menu at the upper right hand side on the homepage. &lt;/p&gt;
